<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Josefin+Sans:100, 300, 400, 700|Julius+Sans+One"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>myBlendology Blend</title>

    <style>
      body { padding: 0px; font-family: 'Julius Sans One', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400; font-size: 13px; background-color: #f9f4f8; height:
      100%; color: rgb(63, 63, 97); } .oilName { color: rgb(105, 121, 67);
      font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; } h4 { font-family: "Josefin
      Sans", sans-serif; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <img src="http://www.myblendology.com/img/logo.png" height="60" />
    <h3>Hey {{recName}}!</h3>
    <h3>{{userName}}
      has sent you the recipe for their custom
      {{blendName}}
      blend.</h3>
    <h3>This blend is based off of a
      {{oils.mood}}
      mood and is comprised of:</h3>

    <h4>* 5 drops of<span class="oilName"> {{oils.base}}</span>
      essential oil.</h4>
    <h4>* 4 drops of<span class="oilName"> {{oils.middle}}</span>
      essential oil.</h4>
    <h4>* 3 drops of<span class="oilName"> {{oils.top}}</span>
      essential oil.</h4>

    <h3>Combine these oils with the filtered water in your aromatherapy
      diffuser, and enjoy!</h3>

    <h4 class="oilName">Want to create your own unique blend? Check out
      <a href="http://www.myblendology.com">myBlendology</a>
      today!</h4>

  </body>
</html>